      <title>迫于欧洲央行压力，Raiffeisen 大幅削减俄罗斯贷款和存款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/raiffeisen-slashes-russia-loans-deposits-due-to-ecb-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧洲央行要求 Raiffeisen Bank International AG 削减其在俄罗斯的风险敞口后，该银行将其在俄罗斯的贷款和存款规模削减了约四分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/raiffeisen-slashes-russia-loans-deposits-due-to-ecb-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 18:45:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举否认者利用 Telegram 召集摇摆州的投票观察员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/election-deniers-use-telegram-to-rally-poll-watchers-in-swing-states</link>
      <description><![CDATA[相信唐纳德·特朗普赢得 2020 年美国大选的阴谋论者正在网上制定计划，监视和拍摄美国摇摆州的投票站，民权组织称此举可能会抑制选民投票率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/election-deniers-use-telegram-to-rally-poll-watchers-in-swing-states</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 18:37:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国最低工资明年将上涨 6.7%，涨幅超过通胀率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/uk-minimum-wage-to-rise-by-6-7-next-year-exceeding-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国最低工资明年将上涨 6.7%，以抵御通胀，这一增长将有助于财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 辩称，周三的预算保护了劳动人民，但可能会使英格兰银行的通胀对抗变得更加复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/uk-minimum-wage-to-rise-by-6-7-next-year-exceeding-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Reeves 竞选顾问帮助 Shein 的 Tang 获取财政访问权限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/reeves-campaign-adviser-helps-shein-s-tang-get-treasury-access</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士称，一位在今年大选活动期间与 Rachel Reeves 密切合作的说客，为中国快时尚公司 Shein 的负责人唐唐纳德 (Donald Tang) 提供了与英国政府高层的接触机会，该公司正在考虑在伦敦证券交易所上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/reeves-campaign-adviser-helps-shein-s-tang-get-treasury-access</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 17:31:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非政府将公务员薪酬提高至 4.7%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/south-african-government-raises-civil-servant-pay-offer-to-4-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非政府将该国公务员的工资涨幅提高至 4.7%，远低于代表 130 万公务员的工会提出的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/south-african-government-raises-civil-servant-pay-offer-to-4-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 17:20:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普为平息波多黎各骚乱而抨击哈里斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/trump-to-prebut-harris-ellipse-speech-biden-to-unveil-ports-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普试图通过关注副总统卡马拉·哈里斯最大的政治弱点之一，来摆脱他在麦迪逊广场花园集会上发表种族主义言论的争议，并使副总统卡马拉·哈里斯将于周二晚上发表的重要讲话无效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/trump-to-prebut-harris-ellipse-speech-biden-to-unveil-ports-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 14:06:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国获得数十亿美元交易，马克龙重启与摩洛哥的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/macron-hits-reset-with-morocco-as-france-signs-billions-in-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙访问了摩洛哥，希望缓和法国与摩洛哥之间经常紧张的关系，并签署了可能价值高达 100 亿欧元的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/macron-hits-reset-with-morocco-as-france-signs-billions-in-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 13:15:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Milei 的改革为首席执行官们带来了对阿根廷的乐观情绪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/javier-milei-s-argentina-revamp-gives-ceos-market-for-profit-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在哈维尔·米莱担任总统的初期，大众汽车公司的南美区负责人对他并不太满意。现在，他和众多商界领袖一样，多年来首次对阿根廷感到鼓舞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/javier-milei-s-argentina-revamp-gives-ceos-market-for-profit-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普盟友班农因藐视国会入狱四个月后获释</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-29/trump-ally-steve-bannon-to-be-released-after-serving-4-months-in-prison-for-contempt-of-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的长期盟友史蒂夫·班农于周二凌晨出狱，此前他因在 2021 年 1 月 6 日美国国会大厦袭击事件国会调查中拒绝服从传票而服刑四个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-29/trump-ally-steve-bannon-to-be-released-after-serving-4-months-in-prison-for-contempt-of-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 04:08:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝索斯称该帖未予认可是为了避免媒体偏见</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/jeff-bezos-explains-post-s-decision-not-to-endorse-a-candidate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司创始人、华盛顿邮报老板杰夫·贝佐斯表示，该报停止支持总统候选人的决定解决了困扰媒体行业的“信誉危机”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/jeff-bezos-explains-post-s-decision-not-to-endorse-a-candidate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 23:44:38 GMT</pubDate>
